  "texts": [
    "In this work, we utilise KD methods (Section 2.4) to train small-sized and efficient language models specialised for processing of clinical texts.",
    "First, we use KD approaches to directly extract compact models from the BioClinicalBERT model; second, we employ continual learning to pretrain existing compact biomedical models (e.g.",
    "BioDistilBERT and BioMobileBERT) using the MIMIC-III notes dataset (Johnson et al. 2016).",
    "In order to distil compact models from BioClinicalBERT, three different KD methods are explored in this work: DistilClinicalBERT, TinyClinicalBERT and ClinicalMiniALBERT (Fig. 3).",
